avegador previene que ataques XSS roben fondos."}}, {"id": "q-w3-5-2", "question": {"EN": "What does the `sol!` macro generate?", "ES": "\u00bfQu\u00e9 genera la macro `sol!`?"}, "options": {"EN": ["Solidity Bytecode", "Rust structs and traits for ABI encoding", "A local blockchain"], "ES": ["Bytecode Solidity", "Structs y traits de Rust para codificaci\u00f3n ABI", "Una blockchain local"]}, "correctIndex": 1, "explanation": {"EN": "It creates type-safe Rust bindings that map to the Solidity definitions provided.", "ES": "Crea bindings de Rust seguros que mapean a las definiciones Solidity provistas."}}, {"id": "q-w3-5-3", "question": {"EN": "Can Alloy in WASM use TCP connections?", "ES": "\u00bfPuede Alloy en WASM usar conexiones TCP?"}, "options": {"EN": ["Yes, natively", "No, browsers restrict raw TCP. It must use HTTP or WebSockets", "Only via proxy"], "ES": ["S\u00ed, nativamente", "No, navegadores restringen TCP crudo. Debe usar HTTP o WebSockets", "Solo v\u00eda proxy"]}, "correctIndex": 1, "explanation": {"EN": "Browser sandboxing forbids raw TCP syscalls. Communication must go through standard Web APIs.", "ES": "El sandboxing del navegador proh\u00edbe syscalls TCP crudas. La comunicaci\u00f3n debe ir por Web APIs est\u00e1ndar."}}]', NULL, 4);
INSERT INTO courses (id, slug, title, description, level, image_url) VALUES ('42fc66b3-35d3-591c-b788-a1e28b718a20', 'rust-solana', '{"EN": "Solana Smart Contracts", "ES": "Contratos Inteligentes en Solana"}', '{"EN": "Master the Anchor framework, accounts model, PDAs, and high-performance DeFi program development on Solana.", "ES": "Domina el framework Anchor, el modelo de cuentas, PDAs y el desarrollo de programas DeFi de alto rendimiento en Solana."}', 'Advanced', 'https://placehold.co/800x500/9945FF/14F195/png?text=Solana+Dev&font=roboto');
INSERT INTO modules (id, course_id, title, "order") VALUES ('63836f98-b84f-562d-b3a5-6f4f740adb6e', '42fc66b3-35d3-591c-b788-a1e28b718a20', '{"EN": "1. The Solana Model", "ES": "1. El Modelo Solana"}', 1);
INSERT INTO chapters (id, module_id, title, content, is_quiz, quiz_data, "order") VALUES ('25b1858b-b579-51ac-9680-5d25a471d5fe', '63836f98-b84f-562d-b3a5-6f4f740adb6e', '{"EN": "Accounts Model vs EVM", "ES": "Modelo de Cuentas vs EVM"}', '{"EN": "# Stateless Programs\nIn Ethereum, contracts hold both code and state (storage variables).\nIn Solana, **Programs are stateless**. They are just logic (code).\nState is stored in separate **Data Accounts**.\n*   When you call a program, you must pass all the accounts it needs to read or write to.\n*   This allows the runtime (Sealevel) to execute transactions in **Parallel**, because it knows exactly which memory regions (accounts) each transaction touches. If Tx A touches Account 1 and Tx B touches Account 2, they run simultaneously on different CPU cores.", "ES": "# Programas Sin Estado\nEn Ethereum, los contratos tienen c\u00f3digo y estado.\nEn Solana, **los Programas son stateless**. Solo l\u00f3gica.\nEl estado vive en **Cuentas de Datos** separadas.\n*   Al llamar un programa, pasas todas las cuentas que necesita.\n*   Esto permite al runtime (Sealevel) ejecutar transacciones en **Paralelo**."}', false, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1);
INSERT INTO chapters (id, module_id, title, content, is_quiz, quiz_data, "order") VALUES ('cd145930-9d64-5e5e-be47-c145a2d8356d', '63836f98-b84f-562d-b3a5-6f4f740adb6e', '{"EN": "The SVM & BPF", "ES": "La SVM y BPF"}', '{"EN": "Solana programs compile to SBF.", "ES": "Los programas de Solana compilan a SBF."}', false, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2);
INSERT INTO chapters (id, module_id, title, content, is_quiz, quiz_data, "order") VALUES ('666ca1c0-06e0-51a9-826b-882bb89dcb23', '63836f98-b84f-562d-b3a5-6f4f740adb6e', '{"EN": "Transactions & Instructions", "ES": "Transacciones e Instrucciones"}', '{"EN": "Anatomy of a transaction.", "ES": "Anatom\u00eda de una transacci\u00f3n."}', false, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3);
INSERT INTO chapters (id, module_id, title, content, is_quiz, quiz_data, "order") VALUES ('3650d9ab-72ee-5663-9fb8-dc1606b9fa93', '63836f98-b84f-562d-b3a5-6f4f740adb6e', '{"EN": "Program Entrypoint", "ES": "Punto de Entrada del Programa"}', '{"EN": "Raw entrypoint without Anchor.", "ES": "Punto de entrada crudo sin Anchor."}', false, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 4);
INSERT INTO chapters (id, module_id, title, content, is_quiz, quiz_data, "order") VALUES ('2fb62b10-fd73-5fde-8f2a-55542013fa49', '63836f98-b84f-562d-b3a5-6f4f740adb6e', '{"EN": "Quiz: Solana Model", "ES": "Quiz: Modelo Solana"}', '{"EN": "Test fundamentals.", "ES": "Prueba fundamentos."}', true, NULL, '[{"id": "q-sol-1-1", "question": {"EN": "Where is state stored in Solana?", "ES": "\u00bfD\u00f3nde se guarda el estado en Solana?"}, "options": {"EN": ["Inside the Program", "In Data Accounts", "In the Block Header"], "ES": ["Dentro del Programa", "En Cuentas de Datos", "En el Block Header"]}, "correctIndex": 1, "explanation": {"EN": "Programs are stateless. Data lives in separate accounts owned by the program.", "ES": "Los programas son sin estado. Los datos viven en cuentas separadas propiedad del programa."}}, {"id": "q-sol-1-2", "question": {"EN": "What allows Solana to execute transactions in parallel?", "ES": "\u00bfQu\u00e9 permite a Solana ejecutar transacciones en paralelo?"}, "options": {"EN": ["Sharding", "Specifying all accessed accounts upfront", "Proof of History"], "ES": ["Sharding", "Especificar todas las cuentas accedidas por adelantado", "Proof of History"]}, "correctIndex": 1, "explanation": {"EN": "By knowing which accounts are touched, the runtime can schedule non-overlapping transactions on different cores.", "ES": "Al saber qu\u00e9 cuentas se tocan, el runtime puede agendar transacciones no solapadas en n\u00facleos diferentes."}}]', NULL, '[{"id": "q-sol-1-1", "question": {"EN": "Where is state stored in Solana?", "ES": "\u00bfD\u00f3nde se guarda el estado en Solana?"}, "options": {"EN": ["Inside the Program", "In Data Accounts", "In the Block Header"], "ES": ["Dentro del Programa", "En Cuentas de Datos", "En el Block Header"]}, "correctIndex": 1, "explanation": {"EN": "Programs are stateless. Data lives in separate accounts owned by the program.", "ES": "Los programas son sin estado. Los datos viven en cuentas separadas propiedad del programa."}}, {"id": "q-sol-1-2", "question": {"EN": "What allows Solana to execute transactions in parallel?", "ES": "\u00bfQu\u00e9 permite a Solana ejecutar transacciones en paralelo?"}, "options": {"EN": ["Sharding", "Specifying all accessed accounts upfront", "Proof of History"], "ES": ["Sharding", "Especificar todas las cuentas accedidas por adelantado", "Proof of History"]}, "correctIndex": 1, "explanation": {"EN": "By knowing which accounts are touched, the runtime can schedule non-overlapping transactions on different cores.", "ES": "Al saber qu\u00e9 cuentas se tocan, el runtime puede agendar transacciones no solapadas en n\u00facleos diferentes."}}]', NULL, '[{"id": "q-sol-1-1", "question": {"EN": "Where is state stored in Solana?", "ES": "\u00bfD\u00f3nde se guarda el estado en Solana?"}, "options": {"EN": ["Inside the Program", "In Data Accounts", "In the Block Header"], "ES": ["Dentro del Programa", "En Cuentas de Datos", "En el Block Header"]}, "correctIndex": 1, "explanation": {"EN": "Programs are stateless. Data lives in separate accounts owned by the program.", "ES": "Los programas son sin estado. Los datos viven en cuentas separadas propiedad del programa."}}, {"id": "q-sol-1-2", "question": {"EN": "What allows Solana to execute transactions in parallel?", "ES": "\u00bfQu\u00e9 permite a Solana ejecutar transacciones en paralelo?"}, "options": {"EN": ["Sharding", "Specifying all accessed accounts upfront", "Proof of History"], "ES": ["Sharding", "Especificar todas las cuentas accedidas por adelantado", "Proof of History"]}, "correctIndex": 1, "explanation": {"EN": "By knowing which accounts are touched, the runtime can schedule non-overlapping transactions on different cores.", "ES": "Al saber qu\u00e9 cuentas se tocan, el runtime puede agendar transacciones no solapadas en n\u00facleos diferentes."}}]', NULL, '[{"id": "q-sol-1-1", "question": {"EN": "Where is state stored in Solana?", "ES": "\u00bfD\u00f3nde se guarda el estado en Solana?"}, "options"